## Standalone Railway FastAPI app

A standalone deployment unit lives in `deploy/railway_fastapi_app`.

It downloads runtime files from Supabase on startup and exposes:

- `GET /health`
- `GET /recommend` (same query contract as `matcher_agent.api.recommend_api`)

See `deploy/railway_fastapi_app/README.md` for required env vars, bucket layout, and Docker build notes.
